{"tid":801372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[需核實］科大又一醜聞 社一浪費三萬蚊食物","createTime":"2018-08-31T14:41:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T01:31:15.000Z","uid":182068,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4b3014f111a906669f3a5fbcc1246f4cb5bce576","tid":801372,"uid":182068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/223512_dc9a301038f79c36a0498dfc424745f2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F223512_dc9a301038f79c36a0498dfc424745f2.png&h=6230fdae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來以為Hall 3浪費200隻雞翼上曬新聞，呢期最威一定係Hall 3，點知有知情人士報料Hall 1放南北（科大酒數）飛機，浪費三萬蚊食物。<br />\n<br />\n科大學生會係咪又要帶人去道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP.S 唔明點解學生會有資格帶人道歉，明明都冇人投票比佢地，學生會憑咩代表科大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1054e7c181ab14ce10b47408999029fdeb4342fa","tid":801372,"uid":113064,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:42:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c6d5fac7a42799a798e1d42b7e7bd578883caa","tid":801372,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:46:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> content farm格式"},{"pid":"4cfbd9b80f7ee9858fa96a54fdabff79e122bfb1","tid":801372,"uid":182068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5c6d5fac7a42799a798e1d42b7e7bd578883caa","tid":801372,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:46:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> content farm格式"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:47:55.000Z","msg":"睇唔到張相？"},{"pid":"653ecab8362492a69108895fc0d845bfdd2f0d5d","tid":801372,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2